bin.Group1d.time_group.code:
class Group1d:
    def time_group(self, nevent, ngroup):
        self.table.group(self.groups)

    def setup(self, nevent, ngroup):
        self.table = sc.data.table_xyz(nevent)
        self.table.coords['group'] = (ngroup * self.table.coords['x']).to(dtype='int64')
        del self.table.coords['x']
        self.contiguous_groups = sc.arange('group', ngroup, unit='m')
        self.groups = sc.arange('group', ngroup, unit='m')
        self.groups.values[0] = 1
        self.groups.values[1] = 0

binned.Lookup.time_create_bool.code:
class Lookup:
    def time_create_bool(self):
        self.hist_bool.coords['x'].values[-1] *= 1.1
        sc.lookup(self.hist_bool, 'x')

    def setup(self):
        self.data = sc.data.binned_x(100_000_000, 10000)
        x = sc.linspace(dim='x', start=0.0, stop=1.0, num=1_000_001, unit='m')
        groups = sc.arange(dim='x', start=0, stop=1_000_000) // 1000 % 5
        self.hist_bool = sc.DataArray(data=groups.astype('bool'), coords={'x': x})
        self.hist_int = sc.DataArray(data=groups, coords={'x': x})
        self.hist_float = sc.DataArray(data=groups.astype('float64'), coords={'x': x})
binned.Lookup.time_create_bool.name: binned.Lookup.time_create_bool
